{"data":[{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"1","text":"Thumelani izimvu njengendlela yokuhlonipha"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"2","text":"Njengenyoni ephaphazelayo"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"3","text":"UMowabi uthi, “Zinzisani ingqondo zenu"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"4","text":"Vumelani iziphepheli zamaMowabi zihlale kini;"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"5","text":"Ngothando, kuzamiswa isihlalo sobukhosi;"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"6","text":"Sizwile ngokuzigqaja kukaMowabi."},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"7","text":"Ngakho-ke abaseMowabi bayalila,"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"8","text":"Amasimu aseHeshibhoni ayabuna,"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"9","text":"Ngakho ngiyakhala njengalokhu iJazeri ikhala,"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"10","text":"Ukuthokoza lokuthaba akusekho ezivinini;"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"11","text":"Inhliziyo yami ikhalela uMowabi njengechacho,"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"12","text":"Lapho uMowabi evela endaweni yakhe ephakemeyo"},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"13","text":"Leli yilizwi uThixo avele eselikhulumile ngoMowabi."},{"book":"U-Isaya","chapter":"16","verse":"14","text":"Kodwa khathesi uThixo uthi: “Phakathi kweminyaka emithathu, njengesisebenzi esibotshwe yisivumelwano singayibala, udumo lukaMowabi labantu bakhe bonke abanengi kuzakweyiswa, njalo abazasinda bakhona bazakuba balutshwana kakhulu njalo bengelamandla.”"}]}